56 TEST_F(EndEffectorTestSuite, config)
57 {
58  ros::NodeHandle nh("end_effector_interface");
59  int id{-1};
60  std::string hw_type;
61 
62  nh.getParam("end_effector_id", id);
63  nh.getParam("hardware_type", hw_type);
64 
65  ASSERT_EQ(id, 0);

67 
68  ASSERT_TRUE(nh.hasParam("button_2/type"));

76 TEST_F(EndEffectorTestSuite, getEndEffectorState)
77 {

79  ASSERT_NE(ee_state, nullptr);
80  ASSERT_EQ(ee_state->getId(), 0);

82 }
83 
84 TEST_F(EndEffectorTestSuite, getButtonState)
85 {
86  auto ee_state = ee_interface->getEndEffectorState();
87  ASSERT_NE(ee_state, nullptr);
88 
89  auto buttons = ee_state->getButtonsStatus();
90  ASSERT_TRUE(buttons.at(0)->type != common::model::EButtonType::UNKNOWN);
91  ASSERT_TRUE(buttons.at(1)->type != common::model::EButtonType::UNKNOWN);
92  ASSERT_TRUE(buttons.at(2)->type != common::model::EButtonType::UNKNOWN);
93 }
